&+LAs you step into the pit in the ground you shiver as an eeri feeling creeps
&+Ldown your spine. You try to shrug it off and continue your descent but it's
&+Lstill there and grows stronger as you penetrate deeper into the Underworld.
&+LYou gasp in horror as you feel yourself loosing footing on the slippery rocks.
&+LYou desperately try to regain your grip but it's too late. As you tumble down
&+Linto the darkness you cannot help but to scream in terror...

